'After booking this holiday i looked over the tripadvisor reviews and wasn't looking forward to my stay. However, when I arrived i was pleasantly surprised and thought people had been reviewing some where else. Food was good, plenty of selections and always stocked up by friendly kitchen and restaurant staff. All hotel staff were friendly, hola everytime they passed you by and talking to the kids. Rooms were clean, comfortable and a welcome break to sit in air con'd room as was heatwave for our first few days - had to watch with a/c as wouldn't come on if doors leading to balcony were not shut properly. Excellent location with everything being a short walk away, but my daughter never wanted to leave the hotel pool!!! Looking forward to going back again. Room Tip: Our room was directly above entertainment area which could have been a problem if you were trying to... See more room tips'